comments:
Every alien letter in this study was a little bit similar to letters i know. For example there was something looking like n, b, o, j, c, x, i. Then i just made something like stories where this words and items appear. For me, this nerf pistol was BOXI, so i thought someone is boxing during a gunfight, and i was repeating this to myself each time i've seen this image. Another example may be this barrel(?) that was BYV? for me. In polish "Bywał" (which means there was something there) sounds exactly like BYV, so i made a sentence
"W tej beczce bywał alkochol" which means "There was alcohol in this barrel".
